Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way I'm gonna let this end so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class A wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Rep?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ESB is over and a new morning has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could these be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're drawing boards and mats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought cardboard boxes were the bottom of the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to the worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined this happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Himeji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be. You really don't need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a lot of fun from the ESB.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we can do anything about losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These drawing boards are definitely usable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they say you can get used to living anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're in art class. It's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the bottom of the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Minami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really need to ask? Of course I'm going to request another ESB!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up, Shimada!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're banned from doing so for another three months!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I just don't want to use these boards anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your breasts won't get in your way, so these are a perfect fit for-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My joints don't work that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I haven't felt this in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "these are a perfect fit!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost... Almost... Just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're burning! You're on fire, Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it got put out by his blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow. Is that all it takes to bring you down, Voyeur?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kudou...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even wore a bra just for you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A really cute one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The body never lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I feel for you, Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry... I forgot that the bracelet broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Voyeur!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please grant summoning permission to Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To remove a bra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I cannot, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess that's as far as our strength goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't accept losing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a defeat is a defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We focused more on pragmatism than scoring high on tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were smart for attacking instead of being distracted by the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost because we let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't change what has already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Results are everything, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that effort is nothing but a means to an end, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do what I needed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I'm just an idiot after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who boast of their own efforts are the most foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But having someone else praise you for your efforts isn't necessarily a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you tried your very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make me proud to be your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right to grieve over your defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't people normally say to do the opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to admit when you've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not being able to do so makes it impossible for you to climb back up after a fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even more impossible for you to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So go on ahead and grieve to your heart's extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after you're done grieving, be sure to set your eyes upon your next goal and move toward it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will comfort you as much as I can when you're grieving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you rather sleep with me or take a bath with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're related by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're done grieving, move forward, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that possibly mean I could still do more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I've made my decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll be taking a bath together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I meant something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for the ESB results.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii, what the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a request to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow us to compete with class A one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I'll have to turn that request down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait another three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't wait that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the rule. I can't break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let it end like this! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider it a request from the rest of us as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot accept such a cowardly victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we technically won,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but they had the upper hand during the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoshita... Kirishima...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That victory is an insult to the top class that represents this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think the rest of the classes will accept this so easily either, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send in my request too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you kids know why the Exam Summoning Battle system was implemented into our school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give way regarding the rules, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still owe you a favor from when the system went berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm responsible for the fact that you were using the prototype bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can make an exception just this once if you're this serious about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exception?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to exchange facilities that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, there are other means of achieving that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rematch with class A?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really can?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old bitch allowed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Akihisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah! We'll beat them into the ground this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and form up a new plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yuuji... It's a bit different this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going solo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, against class A's rep in an exam battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class A's rep? You mean Shouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't exchange facilities if I win,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the principal promised to grant my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're going against the valedictorian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I won't pull you guys down with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, so what'll happen if you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other side gets their wish granted-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, you'll have to return my marriage contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I won't pull you guys down with me." Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my life you're fucking with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't important!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going on a honeymoon right after the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji, I want to make children with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, you have to fucking win this, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouko, take it easy on him, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said not to hold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit! My life is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that I'm gonna lose for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess he's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They granted us a rematch, but there's no way I can beat Kirishima by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you baked cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned it from home economics class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't think they're that good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Hazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! So do you feel a little more confident now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a lot more energetic now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd make a great wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really quite get the hang of it, so I burned a few batches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't give up and kept trying and I succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure I don't give up either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I have anything to lose, so I'll give it everything I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I can do with the time I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll try my best to get even a single point more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a specially permitted rematch between class A's rep, Shouko Kirishima, and class F's Akihisa Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go by the "Sudden Death Rule."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sudden Death Rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exact same question will be given to the contestants,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they are required to solve it at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle ends whenever one of the \Ncontestants answers a question wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The loser will be the one who answered it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, whoever's the first to get a question wrong loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with an endless series of questions here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they'll keep getting harder and harder as they go along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the beginning will be decisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to believe in yourself and do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only cheers people on if it benefits himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question 1:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please answer the question with an idiom that contains the given meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Failing at something you're good at."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an easy question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless Akihisa is literally mentally \Nretarded, he can't screw this one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:11:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like he's having trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both answers are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fucking scare me, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was nervous! I couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question 2:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you calculate the area of a circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! She got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you even get into high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, question 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's edible, but still a long way from what it should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Aki is trying his best now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be great if I could cook \Nhim something as a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to try my best as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Q-Question 30...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When was the 12 level ranking \Nsystem of officials implemented?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both answers are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good going, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to make it this far because I had a feeling these questions would show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not gonna screw up that easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let my guard down for even one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question 31:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the conquerer that began his \Nconquest of the Persian Empire in 334BC
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and defeated the last king of the Achaemenid Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another history question...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both answers are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he got it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Aki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never get this question about \NAlexander the Great wrong ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The easy questions are coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answering is only going to get harder and harder for Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question 32:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of Japan's first era was "Taika."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which year of the Common Era did the reform of the Taika era take place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That question is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a gimme.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them will get this one correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The showdown is delayed until the next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So when exactly did the Taika reforms happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass! How could you forget after we've been through all that crap!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why I'm confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me, you fucking faggot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only remember it according to the "uneventful reforms"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uneventful reforms"... 645AD? 625AD?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which does "uneventful" refer to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uneventful reforms... Uneventful... Uneventful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one? Which one is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over if I get this wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fucking murder him for giving up so easily...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He, he hasn't yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Striker Sigma V!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their answers are different!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, my life's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner is class F's Akihisa Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guessed it right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Aki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one, Akihisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouko, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a promise with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I'd never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, I already got what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go register now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell did you...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kind soul gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No harm in doing a good deed here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Principal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, I'll grant you your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wish... What did you ask from the principal, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, Himeji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to take the placement exam again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:17:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the reason I declared the ESB to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we don't deserve it ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we want you to study some-\Nwhere that's fitting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can now go to the class that matches your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, is this what you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna feel a little lonely, but this is the best choice to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people in this world thinks that grades equate to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what, a person's ability can only go so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:18:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who only care about themselves won't be able to live a fulfilling life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, we all helped each other out as a matter of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something achieved through only one \Nperson's effort isn't really worth that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they understand that, then I can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you'll be able to go to class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you your results later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I messed something up big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you allow me to change that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time allotted is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't change your answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm sure you did fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to... I have to amend that no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to get registered, but we got rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Japanese Civil Code, the male must be at least 18 when he registers for marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unfortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki, have you seen Mizuki yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be hard for you two to see each other now that she's in a different class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji's score on the placement exam will definitely get her into class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji doesn't belong in class F.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be studying with the \Namazing facilities class A has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you think, then okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Akihisa, I don't think things are going to go your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji... Why are you here? Did you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you accepted into class A?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually... I forgot to write my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I got a zero on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here back in class F.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun like we used to, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joys of tear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That goddamned old bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.02,0:22:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth, you little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Himeji get a zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, obviously because she \Nforgot to write her name down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the only one taking the test, so it should be obvious that it's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys blind!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:22:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I never thought I'd live long \Nenough to hear you call me an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, give Himeji's points back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, then let her take the placement exam again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to think you're a real idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're truly one giant idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihisa, you're really stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.13,0:23:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last one I'd expect that from... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
